data.meta_site_name: Judith Dickinson Obituary | September 4, 2023 | Neely Funeral Home - Glenshaw, PA
data.text:
Judith A. Dickinson, age 80 of Shaler Township, on September 4, 2023.

Wife of Robert J. Dickinson.

Mother of Douglas, Darcey Terris, John, Tiffany, Melissa, Tabatha, Gerald, Nicholas and the late Charles and Christopher.

Sister of Daneen Stover and the late Craig Rosenberger.

Grandmother of 18.

No Visitation, A Memorial Service will be held on Saturday September 30th at 11 AM at St. Paul’s United Methodist Church, 1965 Ferguson Rd., Allison Park, PA 15101.

Everyone Please Meet At Church.

In lieu of flowers memorials are suggested to North Hills Community Outreach or to St. Paul’s United Methodist Church.
